{"tid":82940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普稱一中可談判《中國日報》嗆：北京將不惜脫下手套","createTime":"2017-01-16T10:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T11:30:51.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bda33180f8e1958545b8e3f232ea3f2c76f1f4b2","tid":82940,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:46:32.000Z","msg":"川普稱一中可談判《中國日報》嗆：北京將不惜脫下手套  <br />\n<br />\n回應川普在《華爾街日報》的專訪，表示「一個<em><strong>中國」政策是可以談判的，今 (16 日)， 中國大陸兩家具有影響力的媒體發出警告，如果川普一意孤行，那北京將不惜「脫下手套 」(take of the gloves)，犧牲掉台灣。</strong></em> <br />\n<br />\n英語版的《中國日報》在報導中說：「如果川普決定採取這樣的方式 (指一中政策)，那 麼激烈、破壞性的互動將不可避免，因為屆時北京將別無選擇，只能脫下手套。」似乎意 指不排除使用武力。 而《環球時報》也在一篇社論中回應《中國日報》的說法：「中國大陸將加速台灣的統一 ，無情打擊那些主張台灣獨立的人。」稱北京將採取強而有力的對策，來對抗川普損害「 一中」原則的企圖。 <br />\n<br />\n社論也提到，川普對台灣的支持，只是短期為了維護美國政府的利益，這個間炸的戰略可 能會犧牲台灣。 雖然中國大陸各家媒體連環開砲，對川普態度表達不滿，但據香港《明報》報導，北京政 府以中宣部為首的意識形態部門日前已發出禁令，避免出現不必要的「中美輿論大戰」， 要求近期涉及美國的新聞報導，務比遵照「官方口徑」，但似乎還是難以避免雙方隔空交 火。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.cnyes.com/news/id/3687177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F3687177&d=H03ny1%2BlDNTiShrnUE1SD0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=36e1ef4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.cnyes.com/news/id/3687177</a>"},{"pid":"4821da18fc6096087b5362d9b1d3ceb5c1ed581b","tid":82940,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"「脫下手套 」(take of the gloves)<br />\n咩意思？"},{"pid":"4a45512709c7dc25a0645811ff87b08944487d88","tid":82940,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「脫下手套 」(take of the gloves)<br />\n咩意思？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6a5e3b8b44e8ee2670e732b0c108ba64b40dd4b2","tid":82940,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:50:06.000Z","msg":"侵侵意思係話台灣有個價，大陸出得起錢可以吞埋"},{"pid":"4486a05a8f27c3b5f9b145d93160f7076bd5439e","tid":82940,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「脫下手套 」(take of the gloves)<br />\n咩意思？</blockquote><br />\n國民黨+統派=支共既白手套"},{"pid":"e927f8579879e9e521f2954a106d2eaf8740fd5a","tid":82940,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:56:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>「脫下手套 」(take of the gloves)<br />\n咩意思？</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n打飛機"},{"pid":"0a0eb7f4eb4d883f5e9aaaeeb65fc6075f27f2c5","tid":82940,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:58:27.000Z","msg":"Take of<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n報紙佬英文零分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4325f374def96a973cff5f5a982a102bfe95ab6","tid":82940,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:02:16.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64231f75b1510b21c4709a633f0eb9add64d1bd","tid":82940,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:03:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「脫下手套 」(take of the gloves)<br />\n咩意思？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打飛機囉重有得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68cda841c68476f91f95f393777bd08e2981cf2","tid":82940,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:18:01.000Z","msg":"係就快唔好等下個禮拜<br />\n星期五就任喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d47626fe19bee39627c75ebe54f9d6f4510dde","tid":82940,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:22:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>「脫下手套 」(take of the gloves)<br />\n咩意思？</blockquote><br />\n打飛機囉重有得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隔住手套打飛機唔夠爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=